Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:36.18,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,Making a splash, I've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.43,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:45.69,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fsp-1.25}My heart bursting with enthusiasm, I'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:54.11,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:59.87,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,When the summer sun sways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.33,0:01:09.96,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:18.72,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:26.48,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.48,0:01:31.98,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,Making a splash, I've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:36.70,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:41.91,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fsp-1.25}My heart bursting with enthusiasm, I'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:48.21,OP3-English,,0,0,0,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I will remain here...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if we ever meet again some day...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.27,0:02:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...will you call me your friend again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:41.39,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,110)}Scent Of Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:41.39,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)\pos(352,450)}The Seventh Member \Nis Nico Robin!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... We sank one ship...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.69,0:02:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...just one ship belonging to some \N"Bon Clay," a Baroque Works agent.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The other ship was...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get a move on.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So you let them get away...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that I fell for such a cheap trick...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good at running away.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Hina! Watch out!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it makes me angry. I'm going mad!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Angry at your shiftlessness?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.88,0:03:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.51,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! It gives me the tingles! \NThe power of Cage-Cage Fruit!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"Everything that touches \Nmy body will be locked up."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it! Say the killer line! Please say it!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.65,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?! An iron lock?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.28,0:03:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm angry at you, Smoker-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That rings too many bells...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.28,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because... you seem to be quite \Nhappy about Straw Hat getting away.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? Why would I be?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.25,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.55,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said in a formal way,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.84,0:04:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have something important to talk with you about, Daddy... no, Father..."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.92,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As the King of this country, I thought...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"It's also hard to give up on being called Daddy."
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.27,0:04:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot accept your death...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot even shed tears...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.67,0:04:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why... Pell...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.14,0:04:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.95,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Toto-{\i1}san{\i0}? \NYou've been laughing ever since the speech.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez... \NWere you hit by a sandstorm, old man?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.87,0:05:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret. I won't tell you guys what it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.71,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that about...?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.42,0:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Luffy-{\i1}kun{\i0}! \NCome back some time to drink Yuba's water.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.60,0:05:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what're you guys doing? \NDig the well! Dig!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.08,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}When I was little, I had a vision of a treasure map{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.30,0:06:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}and I always searched for that miraculous place{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.81,0:06:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}before someone else could beat me to it{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.52,0:06:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}Every day is now covered with dust{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.87,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}All I can do is yield everything to the time one day{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.59,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}If the world is going to change{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.84,0:06:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say... At any rate, who was the princess talking to?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows and who cares?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.93,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}then take me to the time when I knew nothing{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What Vivi-{\i1}sama{\i0} said makes us happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to respond to it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Though we're nobodies.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't wanna hear it from you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.40,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2\i1\an8}so that my memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.87,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, Alubarna seems to be in bad shape.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us go there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But we also have to restore Yuba quickly,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.09,0:07:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,as it's an important crossroad in the west.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We also have to repair all the \Ncanals along the Sandora River.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What about the casino?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be closed. Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.39,0:07:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why're we giving him special treatment?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.35,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... \NVivi-{\i1}sama{\i0} told us to. What can we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.27,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I heard that he wants \Nto join the Supersonic Duck Squadron.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a camel...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's a camel, isn't he...?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.37,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... Thank you... for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, you're such a hasty one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, with those injuries, I wouldn't \Neven allow you to move around.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. See you, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.00,0:08:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take a long rest once you get home! You got that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.01,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh... Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot this. Here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.97,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, stay put and rest. Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.60,0:08:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the others handle your work.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.65,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and, eat nutritious meals that are \Neasy on the stomach. Don't skip meals...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... I'll be fine, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They're fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather, our ship is slowing down!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.24,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Water's flooding in from the holes. \NWe can't make it all the way out like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.75,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper! Do you still have more panels? \NWe'll be in trouble soon...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Three ships!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.88,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice but to fight, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.55,0:09:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.13,0:09:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp said to keep them since we might \Nbe able to use them for something.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,– They're in our way! \N– We don't need them!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then should we ditch them?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.73,0:09:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, take your positions! \NOnce we pull up, we'll make an all-out attack!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Are we ready?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.20,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the chance. \NLet's go full speed ahead and shake them off!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.33,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Karoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back... to Alubarna!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although my adventure is over,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.97,0:09:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a new challenge, restoring Alabasta, \Nis waiting for me this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.69,0:09:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now Alabasta is like a small, \Nbeat-up ship wandering on the sea...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.61,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no matter how big a wave we face, \Nwe'll never be discouraged...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll push forward, without losing our path...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.33,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...facing straight ahead... vigorously...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.38,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right... just like that wondrous, small ship...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.98,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely be able to see them \Nagain some day, right, Karoo?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Smoker-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.79,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, young lady. Are your legs okay now?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.14,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,P... Please stop talking like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw their new bounties...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For them, these numbers are no surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what his swordsman buddy did?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Roronoa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He slew 100 bounty hunters in Whisky Peak.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.71,0:11:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, he cut down Daz Bonez in Alubarna.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.84,0:11:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Daz...?! That assassin?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.84,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to be a bounty hunter and \Nwas also called that in the West Blue,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but he went under the name \Nof Mr. 1 in Baroque Works.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.81,0:11:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, considering Crocodile had \Nso many famous guys under him,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we should be impressed...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.65,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they lost...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.74,0:12:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a rematch with the Straw Hats some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.03,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the Navy has stopped following us.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.67,0:12:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,– We did shake them off, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.63,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,– Hmm... \N– Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.55,0:12:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know... \NWhat's with those indifferent replies...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.01,0:12:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss her!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be whiny!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanted her to stay with us that badly,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you should've taken her by force!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.23,0:12:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! You're such a savage!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.07,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.15,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mosshead.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.23,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-Sword Style...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.28,0:12:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait, Luffy. \N"Three-Sword Style" isn't an insult.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.73,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Four-Sword Style.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The number isn't exactly the problem...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.28,0:12:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. You know {\i1}natto{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you call {\i1}natto{\i0} rotten, it wouldn't...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we finally made it off of the island!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.16,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.08,0:12:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.09,0:13:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here to avenge your organization?! \NI'll take you on!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.05,0:13:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy attack...! Enemy attack...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.72,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.76,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! She's that beautiful lady!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.15,0:13:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you before not to point \Nsuch dangerous objects at me?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How long have you been on this ship?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.11,0:13:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,These're your clothes, right? \NI'm borrowing them.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you trying to do, Baroque Works?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.83,0:13:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.58,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten what \Nyou did to me, have you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.92,0:13:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! What'd you do to that \Nbeautiful lady, you bastard?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,– Get off the ship immediately.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,– I'm asking you what you did to her!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Don't lie! \NI didn't do anything to you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you did. \NWhat you did to me was unbearable.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take responsibility.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,– What's this "unbearable" thing you did, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,– Who's that and what's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.90,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You'd better take responsibility or...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.90,0:14:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the ship... or we'll call the Navy. \NI'm serious.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.36,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't make sense! \NWhat do you want me to do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.49,0:14:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me... join your crew.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.45,0:14:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.83,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that immediately. It can neutralize the poison from Crocodile's hook.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.01,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's buried in this rubble, \Nhe might survive since he's a rubber man.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.68,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that time that history \Nis the only thing written here...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew...? How mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.03,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This country's history isn't written in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.74,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything about the weapon you \Nwanted must've been written there.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.66,0:14:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, its location, too...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.96,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had told Crocodile about it,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.13,0:15:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the country would've become his \Nat that point. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in such things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.84,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the country and people \Nlive or die, I don't really care.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.11,0:15:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't going to give the weapon \Nto Crocodile from the start.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it... Then why did you come here?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What one expects and what \None hopes are different things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.78,0:15:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What I was seeking was the Rio Poneglyph.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.70,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The only "stone that tells the \Nreal history" among the Poneglyphs
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that are scattered throughout the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Rio Poneglyph...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by the "real history"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.55,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I give up... I've searched for it \Nfor 20 years and I'm out of clues...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.30,0:15:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This place was my last hope... and a failure...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying here like this would \Nbe a fitting end for me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.81,0:16:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Living like this has exhausted me...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to learn the history...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there're too many enemies... \Nto achieve my dream...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you a question...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By any chance... can the untold history be uncovered?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.63,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that the \NPoneglyphs hold that record?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why do we...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second! \NI no longer have a reason to live!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.81,0:16:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to listen to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.57,0:16:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me live then when I wanted to die. \NThat's your crime.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.70,0:17:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no place for me to go or go back to.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.87,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me stay on this ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.41,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see... \NThen I guess we have no choice... Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.00,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She isn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.97,0:17:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mellorine! Mellor...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.24,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.69,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer my questions honestly!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.37,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you one more time. \NWhat's your name?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I'm Usopp. Nice to meet you. \NYeah, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.50,0:17:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, Nico Robin. \NWhat's your occupation?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,An archaeologist.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An archaeologist?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.26,0:17:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I come from a long line of archaeologists.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.93,0:18:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see... That kind of family, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.10,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.05,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I became an archaeologist, \Nand then a wanted criminal.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.23,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I was eight.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.95,0:18:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, I've spent the past \N20 years hiding from the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you were eight...? \NBy yourself all this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.41,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, there was no way for a child \Nto be able to survive alone on the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.91,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in the end, in order to protect \Nmyself and in order to achieve my goal,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.92,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I've chosen to follow various rogues... \NSo that's how it was.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So does that mean that Crocodile \Nwas just another rogue to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.39,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess... in order to get \Ncloser to the Rio Poneglyph...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.10,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rio...?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that, I've become good \Nat doing things behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I'll be able to help you guys, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.23,0:18:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...? You're full of confidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.52,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you good at?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassination.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.12,0:19:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! This investigation has \Nconcluded that she's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you guys listening?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.89,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Being dealt with so easily... How pathetic!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.46,0:19:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She was the vice president of a \Ncrime syndicate until just recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How are we gonna let such a woman join us?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.30,0:19:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you could deceive idiots, \Nyou can't deceive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.30,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pull any weird stunts, I'll kick you out!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.94,0:19:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.69,0:19:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.57,0:19:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some of Crocodile's jewelry with me...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.57,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I love you, sister!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.20,0:19:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami's been suckered.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an evil trick.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's completely following that woman's lead.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, love... Floating love...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.96,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm driftwood that just lays its \Nburnt-to-a-crisp body in that stream...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.43,0:20:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm driftwood that has been struck \Nby the thunderbolt that is your beauty
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.35,0:20:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and caught in a raging torrent...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.60,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Snack for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And his reaction is no surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.48,0:20:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... We just have to consider that \Nhe was a lost cause from the start...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.02,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case... now that it's come to this, \Nthe two of us are the last holdouts.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.78,0:20:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, they're so simple-minded, \Nor should I say lax.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.33,0:20:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Usopp!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.03,0:20:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.42,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I call you "Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}"? \NOr should it be "Robin-{\i1}san{\i0}"...?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.26,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Which should it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where're you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.43,0:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... she's great...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.31,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got an adult charm, \Nwhich is different from Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.40,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship is nice... Is it always lively like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... It is.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.37,0:21:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that woman up to...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Navigator... \NIs it smooth sailing right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.68,0:21:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wind, weather... Both no problem! \NIt's going very smoothly, Sis!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You definitely got jewelry from her, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji! Isn't our snack ready?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.60,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.02,0:21:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! Me too! Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.99,0:21:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My grave...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.55,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}Doko ni mukatte hashireba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.22,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}Motto suteki na ashita ni aeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:15.27,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}Kaji o totte mune ni shimatta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.19,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}Kiseki no chizu o hirogeta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:21.19,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}Sora o mezashite yume o sagashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.40,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}Michi ni mayotta toki mo aru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.15,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}Yume ja nakute kimi to deatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:29.87,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}Suteki na jibun o mitsuketa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:32.78,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}Chiisana yuuki kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:36.12,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}ookina mono te ni shita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:41.54,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.4\fsp-2}"Negai" o ima koso "chikai" ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:45.26,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.4}Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:49.05,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}Mirai no monogatari o egakou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.34,0:22:54.31,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.4}Atarashii kaze ni subete no omoi nosete ima...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:57.27,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.4}Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.27,0:23:00.31,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:04.86,ED8-Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.4}Doko made mo oikakete Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.55,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}Which direction should I run towards
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:12.22,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}to see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:15.27,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}I took the helm and opened the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:18.19,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}miraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.19,0:22:21.19,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}I aimed for the sky and sought out my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:24.40,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.15,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}It wasn't a dream; when I met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.15,0:22:29.87,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur0.4}I discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.87,0:22:32.78,ED8-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur0.4}With just a bit of courage,
